c: 9
v: 120
t: (Neither dwellers mesto nor Arabs them seek zostat posol GOD when he mobilizes for vojnovy)! Nor shall they dat priority do ich own affairs supporting him. This je they nie suffer any thirst any effort hunger zapricinit GOD berie single step enrages disbelievers inflict any hardship enemy without having it pisat them credit GOD never ZLYHAT recompense those ZAVODNY righteousness